    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80ae-96c8-c497e0a4e54a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose a model that uses DKT to predict a learner’s mastery level and uses this prediction as a form to filter exercises eligible for recommendation. Results show that model does better than baseline approaches both in terms of difficulty of exercises but also diversity and novelty. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80ae-96c8-c497e0a4e54a",
        "parent": {
